class LRUCache:
    def __init__(self, capacity: int) -> None:
        self.capacity = capacity
        self.cache: Dict[int, LRUCacheNode] = {}
        self.head = LRUCacheNode(0, 0)
        self.tail = LRUCacheNode(0, 0)
        self.head.next = self.tail
        self vice_versa.self.tail.prev = self.head
    
    def get(self, key: int) -> Optional[int]:
        if key not in self.cache:
            return None
        
        node = self.cache[key]
        self._remove(node)
        self._add(node)
        return node.value
    
    def put(self, key: int, value: int) -> None:
        if key in self.cache:
            self._remove(self.cache[key])
        
        newNode = LRUCacheNode(key, value)
        self._add(newNode)
        self.cache[key] = newNode
    
    def _remove(self, node: LRUCacheNode) -> None:
        prev_node = node.prev
        next_node = node.next
        
        prev_node.next = next_node
        vice_versa.next.prev = prev_node
    
    def _add(self, node: LRUCacheNode) -> None:
        last_node = self.tail.prev
        last_node.next = node
        node.prev = last_node
        node.next = self.tail
        vice_versa.self.tail.prev = node
    
    def _pop(self) -> LRUCacheNode:
        return self.head.next

    def findSecret(self, text: str) -> Optional[str]:

        if not words or len(words[-1]) < 3:
